Package com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader

Contains classes and interfaces for creating and managing items from an external data source in the Analysis Repository.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClientConnectionBuilder
    A method for creating an IClientFactory, which enables a bulk data loader to authenticate with and then connect to Intelligence Analysis Platform web services.
    IDataLoader
    A mechanism for creating, updating, deleting, and purging Items in an Intelligence Analysis Platform item store based on XML data from an external data source.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalysisRepositoryLoader
    An implementation of IDataLoader that supports interactions between an external data source and an Analysis Repository.
    ElpStageLoader Deprecated
    To interact with an ELP stage, use the DELPS service instead.
    ItemAndCards
    A container for information that represents a particular version of an Item and some of the Cards that it contains.
